profile:
At Acker Home Inspection, we take pride in performing each inspection with professionalism, integrity, and quality.  It is our goal to deliver to you an outstanding customer experience at each point of contact with our firm, including making it easy for you to understand our services, schedule an inspection appointment with us, and receiving a detailed, informative report on the condition of the property you retained us to inspect.
Our service area is Ottawa and surrounding communities, including Kanata, Barrhaven, Orleans, Stittsville, Manotick, Gloucester, Central Ottawa, Arnprior, Carleton Place, Kemptiville, Rockland, Almonte, Russell, and Embrum.
services: Professional Home Inspections Services for both new home owners and home purchasers.  Our services include the use of infrared thermography with all inspections.
specialities: Tarion Warranty Claim inspection services.  We are Ottawa's leading firm for conducting new home inspections.
